sku: Proline Seamless Old Granite Cleft Stone
meta_description: Proline Seamless Old Granite Cleft Stone
short_description: Seamless Skins
summary: Proline is the innovator of the Seamless Texturing system. The very first Seamless Texture to roll of a production line was Proline's Old Granite Cleft Stone. It was followed by Roman Slate, especially designed for Caesar Palace in Las Vegas. Now, these are the standards in the industry. All others are imitations of the original. All Proline skins are made of the highest grade urethane in a unique process that resuls in highly durable stamping tools. Proline tools are carefully hand-built and represent a life-like stone and texture. As an applicator, you will appreciate how light and easy our mats are to use. All Seamless Textures include handles, with the exception of touch up mats. All patterns are available in 5' x 5', 4' x 4', 3' x 3', 2' x 4' and 20" x 20" for touch up. We also offer our touch up mats in a super-flex material for added flexiblility into tight places. You can have the look of natural stone, with the durability and low cost of concrete. Check out our many patterns. Easy to install - the only hard part is choosing between all the beautiful patterns.

short_description: Dura-Color Hardeners
summary: Dry-shake Color Hardeners come as powders that are hand broadcast onto the freshly placed concrete and then worked into the surface with a float or trowel. Proline's Dura Color Hardener is a uniform, streak-free concrete color hardener that's durable enough for high traffic areas. In addition to adding color to concrete, it makes a great base for stamped concrete. Available in 42 beautiful colors.

short_description: Water-Based Antiquing Wash
summary: Newly introduced by Proline, EZ-Tique Water Based Acrylic Antiquing Wash is taking the industry by storm. This versatile coloring agent is easily applied and will hold fast to any textured concrete surface. This powder is designed to mix with water and be applied as a liquid wash coat. EZ-Tique can be used to revitalize a weathered concrete surface or add an antique color to a freshly textured surface. It goes on quickly and easily and can be removed readily for greater control of the coloring process. This product is water-based, non-hazardous and zero V.O.C. EZ-Tique comes in 42 standard colors, as does Proline's Color Hardener and Antique Release. It comes in a 3 lb. pail and covers about 2,000 - 3,000 square feet per container, making this product extremely affordable.

short_description: Chemical Acid Stain
summary: Chemical, or Reactive Stains, can be applied to new or old, plain or colored and stamped concrete surfaces. Chemical Stains penetrates and permanently stains new or existing concrete and wears only as the concrete wears. Use a reative stain for creative faux finishes, permanent and veriegated colors, no chipping or peeling and lasting results. Available in 9 standard colors. Proline also offers a variegated water-based acrylic stain- see EZ-Accent.

short_description: Water-Based Stain
summary: Proline Dura Color EZ-Accent is a water-based acrylic stain that is specially formulated to accent any decorative concrete surface. It is a translucent stain that is designed to blend with the base color over which it is applied. EZ-Accent is quickly and easily applied to decorative concrete flatwork, vertical surfaces and rockscaped for accent colors and natural-looking variations. There are 15 standard EZ-Accent colors. Sold in 1 gallon containers with coverage between 200 and 500 square feet per gallon.

short_description: Size 		 		 			: 		 		 			16" X 16" 		 	 	 		 			Tools 		 		 			: 		 		 			16TAM
summary: Proline manufactures the finest Tampers in the market. This patented tool offers easy dismantel, an extra long grip, composite handle, removable locking pin, rounded corners and edges and self-aligning base. Most important, our Tampers have a shock-absorbing flexible coupling to take the pressure off the shoulders of the installer. Also available in a 12" size.

meta_description: Proline brings the popular look of slate to the decorative concrete world. The ever-classic Ashlar Stone look dates as far back as the 12th century and is found in most western architecture. We offer a variety of background textures, including this beauti
description: Proline brings the popular look of slate to the decorative concrete world. The ever-classic Ashlar Stone look dates as far back as the 12th century and is found in most western architecture. We offer a variety of background textures, including this beautiful New England Slate. This stamp consists of a 3-part system to allow a more open pattern. Color-coded to reduce repeats, these quality mats both heavy duty and tight fitting for a perfectly balanced fit.

description: Proline's new English Ashlar replicates English masonry work dating back to the 12th century. The heavy textured surface gives this stamping tool the natural and rugged look common in old European structures. Achieve the look of traditional Old World architecture with the low cost and durability of concrete. Central Concrete Accessories , a full stocking distributor of Proline products in Western Canada, asked Proline to develop this version of an Ashlar pattern for Chad Kroeger, the lead singer of the band Nickleback. A two part stamping tool, consisting of an "A" & "B" set.

Our Bellagio Custom Band Tool makes a prestigic statement as an accent piece to band around any Seamless Texture or patterned stampwork. Flamed Granite texture accents the background of this lovely piece.

short_description: Size: 17" x 36" Tools: BK200, BK200F, SKB, HT4S, HT8S, W38T
summary: A running bond pattern is brick with the joins in each row centered on the bricks in the row below. Proline offers a traditional used brick size of 4" x 8" in this Running Bond pattern. We also offer the same size brick in a Herringbone and Basketweave pattern.

short_description: Size: 16" x 32" Tools: BK300, BK300F, SKB, HT4S, HT8S, W14R
summary: The Basketweave pattern is a pattern made up of pairs of bricks placed in a square grid so that the join between each pair is perpendicular to the join of the four pairs around it. Proline offers a tradional used brick size of 4" x 8" in a Basketweave pattern. Love the look of Used brick? Check out our Herringbone and Running Bond patterns as well as our Brick Band Tools.

short_description: Size: 37" x 50" Tools: BK400, BK400F, 2LS, HT8S, WV
summary: Proline offers a larger size paver in a Herringbone pattern. The pavers measure 6" wide and 11.75" in length. The background texture is Limestone.

short_description: Size: 24" x 37" Tools: BK100, BK100F, SKB, HT4S, W38T
summary: Herringbone pattern refers to a pattern of columns of short parallel lines with all the lines in one column sloping one way lines in adjacent columns sloping the other way. Proline offers a tradtional used brick in a Herringbone pattern. Brick sizes are a typical 4" x 8" in size. We also offer brick patterns in a running bond and basketweave pattern, as well. Couple this look with any of our Brick Band Tools for a fabulous finish. Easy to color with our new EZ-Accent Water Based Acrylic Stain, your neighbors will not be able to tell your stamped concrete from the real thing.

short_description: Size: 20" x 44" Tools: CS100, CS100F, 2FG, 2FGF, W14R, HT12S, HT4S
summary: Old Cobblestone has the look of an Old World classic. The stones run in a running bond or offset pattern. There is a variant in the size of the stones with the largest stone measuring 5" x 8 1/2". This pattern can be widely used for driveways, patios, walkway and interiors.

short_description: Size: 24" X 37" Tools: CS200, CS200F, 2FG, 2FGF, W14R, HT12S, HT4S
summary: Proline's Herringbone Old Cobble Stone offers a tradional 4" x 8" size Granite Cobble Stone in a classic Herringbone Pattern. This pattern will give a stunning Old World look to any patio, driveway or walkway. Proline stamps are preferred by contractors due to their precision, lighter weight and disctinctive beauty. Decorative concrete offers lower costs, higher durability and inherent strength.

This pattern offers larger, wider cobblestones that vary in size from 8" x 9.5" to a larger stone of 8" x 8.5" in a running bond pattern. The benefit of decorative concrete versus natural stone is lower cost, higher durability and inherent strength and endurance.

short_description: Size: 23" X 43" Tools: CS350, CS350F, 2CUTSTONE, 2CUTSTONEF, W14R, HT12S, HT4S
summary: The beautiful look of Old World Cobble offered in a cut stone version, with it's own unique background texture. What a lovely accent to any area in your home. Proline offers precision fit, a lighter stamp and a distinctive look. Cobblestone range in size from 5.5" x 5" to as large as 5.5 x 8" in a running bond pattern. As with all Proline patterns, this stamp is offered in a thin flex for edges, against walls and walkways. Combine this stamp with any of our Border Art or Band Tools for a truly unique impression.

summary: Originally designed to replicate the European Fan Palm Tree design, our European Fan Small Stone stamping pattern consists of 6 rows of Old World Cobblestones. We offer this stamp in a thin-flex mat as well, for finishing against walls and edges. This stamps creates a very unique overall fan pattern. Stones in this pattern average 5" -5.5". Looking for this same pattern in a larger scale? Check out our European Fan Large Stone or our Fishscale Granite for an added twist to an old favorite.

short_description: Size: 28" X 52" Tools: EF200, EF200F, 2BL, 2BLF, W14R, ST
summary: Proline pays homage to an Old World traditional favorite in it's replication of the European Fan Large Stone. Proline is proud to offer our European Fan Large Stone, as a larger scale variation to our European Fan Small Stone. This pattern consists of three rows of granite cobblestones that average 9.5" x 10" in size.

short_description: Size: 21" X 51" Tools: EF300, EF300F, 2FG, 2FGF, W14R, ST
summary: Proline's Fishscale Granite is a variation of the European Fan. Each stamp offers five rows of cobblestones in a "V" shape, or introverted pattern. Proline patterns can give you the look of real Old World classics with the low cost and durability of concrete.

short_description: Tools: SA1001 & SA1002
summary: The Yuko Fan is a smaller scale of our European Fan pattern. The average size stone varies from the smallest, measuring 2.5" x 2" up to the largest at 3.5" x 3.5" in size. This tool also comes in gang tool version as well.

short_description: Tools: SA1101, SA1102
summary: Proline is now offering Hand Sculpted Accent Pieces for decorative concrete. This series of two Eagles will truly express your love of nature and country. The bald eagle is the only eagle unique to North America and is our country's national emblem. Our new Accent Pieces are easy to install and inexpensive to purchase. Use our EZ-Accent Water Based Stain to color or simply add our EZ-Tique Antiquing system for dimension. Each eagle is also sold separately. See SA1101 & SA1102.

short_description: Size: 24.5" W x 11.5" H Tools: SA1200
summary: The Texas Longhorn Steer is a living symbol of the Old West. No other animal has kept the past than the Longhorn Steer. These great animals carved a path in history that will live forever. The history, tradtition and passion of these animals are celebrated around the world. One of many in our Wildlife series of Hand Sculpted Accent Pieces, this stamp will be a great addition to any stamped concrete area. Measuring 24.5" in width and 11.5" in height, this piece is sure to make a statement. Consider a combination of other Proline products, such as our Boardwalk Wood planks and our Wild Mustang Border Art. All of our Sculpted Accent Pieces are easy to install and inexpensive to purchase, for a truly unique look to set your stamp job apart from all others.

short_description: Size: 11" x 17" Tools: SA1300
summary: Brand New from Proline! Our hand sculpted Bear is beautifully carved and artfully detailed. Combine this stamp with any of our other pieces in this Wildlife series to portray your love of nature.

short_description: Tools: SA2000, SA2001, SA2003
summary: Of all insects, none elicit pleasure and curiosity more readily than the butterfly and are among the most beautiful and marvelous creatures in all of nature. Representations of butterflies are seen in Egytian frescoes, dating more than 3500 years ago. You too can add these beautiful and graceful creatures to any area, inside or out, with Proline's new Hand Sculpted Accent Pieces. We offer a set of three butterflies, however, each stamp is sold individually as well (see SA2001, SA2002 & SA2003). Very easy to install, these pieces are perfect to color with our new EZ-Accent Water Based Stains. Consider these pieces in combination with our Border Art stamps, such as the Garden Rose.

short_description: Tools: SA3101 & SA3102
summary: Our new Sculpted Accent series include these two fanciful Dolphins stamps. The single Dolphin measures 18" W x 5" H and the double Dolphin measures 21" W x 7.5" H. These stamps work wonderful with our Dolphin Border Art or by themselves. What a wonderful addition to a pool area, or as an accent to a kitchen backsplash area. The possibilities are endless. Easy to install and inexpensive to purchase, our Sculpted Accent pieces are easily colored with our new EZ Accent Water Based Acrylic Stains. Each piece also sold separtely (See SA3101 & SA3102).

short_description: Tools: SA3102
summary: The double Dolphin measures 21" W x 7.5" H. Use as a single accent piece or with our Dolphin Border Art (See BA110), this new Sculpted Accent Piece from Proline can be the perfect addition to your home or pool area. Easy to color with our new EZ Accent Water Based Acrylic Stains, let this stamp reflect your fanciful side. Also see our Single Dolphin in the series (SA3101).

short_description: Size: 12.5"W x 11.5"H Tools: SA1001 & SA1002
summary: The elk is the second largest member of the deer family, second only to the moose. A native of North America, the elk is found in many states. Proline offers this beautiful Hand Sculpted Accent Piece of a native Elk postured in a "bugling" position. The elk "Bugle" is one of the most distinctive calls in nature. Combine this stamp with our moose for a real "wildlife" look. Easy to install, inexpensive to purchase and simple to color with our EZ-Accent Water Based Stains - or simply add our EZ-Tique Water Based Antiquing system for great texture. This stamp is also sold as a set with the Moose.

short_description: Size: 9.5" W x 9.5" H Tools: SA1101, SA1102

Proline offers two versions of the American Bald Eagle- this statuesque head image as well as one in flight (See SA1102). Measuring 9.5" in height and width, this piece makes a bold statement.

short_description: Size: 3 ft. diameter Tools: MD7301
summary: Apollo is the greek sun god, bringing life-giving heat and light to earth. This sun is set inside a 3 ft. diameter stamp. The background texture is Italian Slate. Use our reactive stains or our new easy-to-use water-based acrylic stains, EZ-Accent. Add this beautifully carved stamp to any home or business for a real "sizzling" look. Proline also offers this same look as a skin, without the circle. See "Flaming Sun". If you love sun patterns, also check out our brand new Seamless Design, Spiral Sun.

short_description: Tools: MD7401
summary: You'll never loose your way with Proline's new Compass Medallion. In lieu of extensive saw cutting, this 4 ft. diameter stamp will make application a breeze. Our new water-based acrylic stains and antiquing system makes it easy to color. Look at a chart of available colors under Color/Stains- EZ-Accent & EZ-Tique.

short_description: Size: 4 ft. diameter Tools: MD7402
summary: The Nautical Star were first tattooed on early sailors as a good luck symbol in hope of returning home. This 4 ft. Medallion is easy to color with our new EZ-Accent water-based stain.

short_description: Size: 4 ft. diameter Tools: MD7403
summary: The five point Star can be traced to ancient Greece, with magical associations. This piece is 4 ft. in diameter. Easy to color with Proline's new EZ-Accent water-based acrylic stain.

short_description: Tools: MD7404

Diameter Medallion will make a lovely accent piece to any home, patio or driveway. Try our new water-based acrylic stains for easy coloring. Comprised of a combination of Limstone, Quartzite and Roman Slate textures.

short_description: Tools: MD7405

short_description: Size: 65'' x 65'' Tools: MD7406

A beautiful addition to any home or business and easy to color with Proline's EZ-Accent and EZ-Tique water based stains and antiquing system.

short_description: Size: 4 ft. Diameter Tools: MD7407

short_description: Size: 13' in Diameter Tools: MD7130

short_description: Tools: ECSRT1000 Available Size / Series: ECSCT2000- CURVED TOOL, ECSHT3000-HALF TOOL, ECSFT4000-FULL TOOL, ECSDT5000-DOUBLE TOOL
summary: Proline continues to create and introduce innovative ideas and techniques into the decorative concrete market. This series consists of 5 different stamping tools. Those 5 tools can produce a radial that can go out as far as the imagination, along with a serpentine, straight cobble or band tool designs. Totally unique and affordable, Proline's Cobble Series is unlike any stamping tool on the market. This piece, by itself, will create a cobble circle.

short_description: Tools: ECSCT2000 Available Size / Series: ECSCT1000- ROUND TOOL, ECSHT3000-HALF TOOL, ECSFT4000-FULL TOOL, ECSDT5000-DOUBLE TOOL
summary: One of five pieces of our new European Cobble Series, this tool will work as part of an infinite radial or by itself as a Serpentine pattern. Thomas Jefferson is credited with bringing the Serpentine brick pattern to American architecture. Proline has produced a very unique stamping tool series of 5 tools that can not only produce a Serpentine design, but a radial, straight cobble or band tools, as well. This graceful wavy pattern will add charm and elegance to any home or business. This series gives the concrete professional the advantage of an afforable tool series with multiple uses and patterns.

short_description: Size: 26" x 26" Tools: KBSOCT1000
summary: Another new product from Proline and premiered at the World of Concrete 2010, this radial stamping tool is made up of 4 individual pieces including this center pieces. From these 4 pieces in the series, a radial of infinite proportions can be stamped. The other unique quality of these tools is that many more stamping patterns can be produced from these tools, making this series an incredible cost-efficient purchase.

short_description: Size: 24.5" x 28" Tools: KBSCT2000
summary: Brand new from Proline, this Octagon Radial is unique because Proline has designed a radial stamp that has no limits in size. This is one of 4 parts needed to create the Octagon Radial.

short_description: Size: 24" x 20" Tools: KBSST3000
summary: Part of a 4 part series, making an Octagon of infinite dimensions, this Rectangle can also double as a band tool by itself.

short_description: Size: 24" x 40" Tools: KBSST4000
summary: Octagon Radial Double Rectangle. This is part of a 4 piece series that can make an Octagon Radial that goes our to infinite proportions. By itself, it can make a band tool or straight cobble.

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS100, RS100F, 2SL, 2SLF, W38R, ST
summary: Looking for a natural stone look with the durability of concrete? Our Random Sandstone comes in 3 versions-including this groutable rendition. This variation of our Random Sandstone can be grouted for a more natural look. Each stamp contains 6 natural looking stones ranging in size from approx. 8' x 10" to 13" to 17.5". See RS120 & RS130 for other versions of this pattern.

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS120, RS120F, 2SL, 2SLF, W38R, ST
summary: Looking for a natural stone look with the durability of concrete? Our Random Sandstone comes in 3 versions-including this wide joint rendition. Each stamp contains 6 natural looking stones ranging in size from approx. 8' x 10" to 13" to 17.5". For this same look, on a "Grander" scale, check out our Grand Sandstone Groutable.

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS130, RS130F, 2SL, 2SLF, W14R, ST
summary: Looking for a natural stone look with the durability of concrete? Our Random Sandstone Hammered Edge is one of our most popular patterns. This stamp comes in 3 versions (see Random Sandstone Groutable & Random Sandstone Wide Joint). Each stamp consists of 6 natural stones ranging in size from 9" x 10.5" to the larger 13" x 19". As with all Proline patterns, this stamp comes in a thin-flex mat for finishing edges and against walls. This is a favorite among home owners, as it looks beautiful with any type of home design. Looking for the same type of pattern on a larger scale? Check out our Grand Sandstone 1/4:" joint stamp.

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS135, RS135F, 2FG, 2FGF, W14R, ST
summary: This piece is a Canyon Stone in a random stone pattern. The stones are beautifully complimented with a Flamed Granite background. The edges of the stones are lightly chiseled. Natural stone with the durability of concrete-the true beauty of decorative stamped concrete. Color this piece with any of our easy to apply water-based acrylic stains for a layered, natural stone look. The rock size in this piece vary from a smaller 9.5" x 13.5" to a larger 13.5" x 21.5".

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS140, RS140F, W14R
summary: This is no "Garden" variety - this unique pattern will make your neighbors envious. Consisting of natural random stones surrounded by pebblestones, this pattern will delight any garden path or walkway. A single tool application that also comes in a thin-flex mat for stamping against walls and walkway edges. Guaranteed to turn any area into an enchanting garden.

short_description: Size: 41.5" x 41.5" Tools: RS150, RS150F, 2LC, 2LCF, W14R, ST
summary: Designed for the river bottom at the Wild Animal Park in San Diego, CA, this pattern resembles real river rock. Corners of the stone are rounded and the average size of the rocks range from 4" x 5" to 7" x 9". The groutlines are extra deep for that true, river rock semblance. Coloring with our new EZ Accent water based acrylic stain is a breeze.

short_description: Size: 34" x 36" Tools: RS160, RS160F, 2BE, 2BEF, W14R, HT12H
summary: Love the look of natural random stones with the rugged texture of slate? Proline's Random Belgium Slate gives you stones ranging in size from approx.8" x 10" to 12" by 18". Each stone has a lightly hammered edge and defined grout lines for a natural quality. A single tool application and, as wth all Proline's patterns, we offer this pattern in a thin-flex mat for finishing against walls and walkway edges. Belgium Slate adorns the background of these stately stones. Consider accenting this piece with any of our many Band and Border Tools.

meta_description: One of our Random Stone collection, Proline's Sedona Stone is a randomly placed stone pattern. This is a two-part system, as each piece is slightly varied for a more random look to the pattern. Light Sandstone adorns the background and the edges of these
description: One of our Random Stone collection, Proline's Sedona Stone is a randomly placed stone pattern. This is a two-part system, as each piece is slightly varied for a more random look to the pattern. Light Sandstone adorns the background and the edges of these stones are roughly chiseled. If you love the look of natural stone but want the low cost and durability of concrete, then consider this piece as an addition to your home or business. Stone sizes vary from 12" x 14" to 14" x 19" on the A side.

summary: Whoever slated the phrase "your home is your castle" must have had Proline's Castle Stone in mind. This stunning pattern is a single tool application. As with all Proline patterns, this pattern also comes in a thin-flex mat for finishing edges and stamping against walls. Stones, ranging in size from 9" x 12" to 13.5" x 22.5", have hammered edges and defined grout lines for a more natural and random look. Proline's Bluestone Texture accents the background of this eye-catching piece. With Proline's help, you can transform this relic of the past into a modern-day masterpiece. Check out our Fleur-de-lis Border Art to capture a French theme. Our perhaps our English Rose for a British feel. The possibilies are endless.

description: A natural stone with a exclusive characteristic. Our Santa Fe Random Pattern comes in 3 sizes of stone- small, medium and large- with a light sandstone background. What makes this pattern unique is that the 3 sizes are interchangeable- for a truly random natural look. Consider using our Santa Fe Random Stone Small in walkways, leading to large drive-way areas using a mixture of Santa Fe Stone Medium and Santa Fe Stone Large. Scale up or down- it's so easy with Proline's Santa Fe Stone Series. Added bonus: each size comes in 2 different color-coded patterns, allowing for a more random pattern. Also see: Santa Fe Stone Medium & Santa Fe Stone Large. There are a total of 12 stamp patterns in this series.

summary: Elk Landscape Seamless Design The Elk is the larges species of deer in the world. Proline's new Elk Landscape is so life-like that you can almost hear the bugle of the Elk echo through the mountains. This scene is easy to install because it is set inside of a Seamless Slate texture skin. Proline offers a similiar scene with a Bear, as well.

Proline's new Seamless Design, Bear Landscape, is so life-like you can almost feel the slow and clumsy walk with a swing to its head of this stately Bear. This scene is simple to install because it is set inside of a Seamless Texture skin with a slate texture. Proline offers a similiar scene with an Elk, as well.

short_description: Tools: 5OG,4OG,3OG,24OG,2OG,2OGF
summary: Seamless Old Granite Cleft Stone Talk about innovation - Old Granite Cleft Stone was the very first seamless texture ever produced. It started an entire industry of seamless texture skins. Seamless textures are preferred by contractors and homeowners because they are easy to apply, can be done in less time than pattern concrete, allows for a clean look with less grout lines and produces a long lasting beautiful addition to your home. Granite is a plutonic rock of the Earth's crust, formed by the cooling of magma into a lovely textured stone. Developed from real rock, Proline's Seamless Old Granite Cleft Stone resembles the natural stone adding the benefit of lower cost, higher durability and inherent strength and endurance. Old Granite Cleft Stone has a "signature" vein that sets it apart from all others. A perfect accent to driveways, patios, walkways, kitchen countertops and interior floors - this pattern will surely leave a lasting impression. We offer our seamless textures in 6 varieties of sizes and textures. See:, 4OG, 3OG, 24OG, 2OG,2OGF. Also see our Border Art stamps and Band Tools for accent tools.

Seamless textures are preferred by contractors and homeowners because they are easy to apply, can be done in less time than pattern concrete, allows for a clean look with less grout lines and produces a long lasting beautiful addition to your home. Granite is a plutonic rock of the Earth's crust, formed by the cooling of magma into a lovely textured stone. Developed from real rock, Proline's Seamless Old Granite Cleft Stone resembles the natural stone adding the benefit of lower cost, higher durability and inherent strength and endurance. Old Granite Cleft Stone has a "signature" vein that sets it apart from all others. A perfect accent to driveways, patios, walkways, kitchen countertops and interior floors - this pattern will surely leave a lasting impression. We offer our seamless textures in 6 varieties of sizes and textures. See:, 4OG, 3OG, 24OG, 2OG,2OGF. Also see our Border Art stamps and Band Tools for accent tools.

summary: Coquina Stone is a sedimentary rock mainly composed of seashells or coral that takes years to produce and is expensive to process. Proline's Seamless Coquina Stone can provide you a charming aquatic texture with the low cost, durability and endurance of concrete. This piece is perfect for pool areas, as it has a natural traction when wet to prevent slippage. The Seamless Texture design, an innovation of Proline, allows for easy installation. As with all our Seamless Textures, with the exception of touch up skins, handles are included for increased movability. We offer this pattern in a choice of 6 different sizes and flexibilities. Proline can give you the natural look of Limestone without the problems. With our stamping system, you can enjoy the beauty of Limestone with the durability and low cost of concrete. Seamless textures, an original design of Proline, allows for a flowing pattern free of grout lines for easy care. Add any of our Border Art Tools or Band Tools, for a truly unique design. As with all our Seamless Textures mats, we offer Limestone in a variety of 6 different sizes and density. See: 4LS, 3LS, 24LS, 2LS. 2LSF

short_description: Size: 5' X 5' Tools: 5BL,4BL,3BL,24BL,2BL, 2BLF
summary: Blue Stone is a rugged pattern. Large deposits of natural Blue Stone are found near Derbyshire, England. The term bluestone is also used for the dolerite stones at Stonehenge. This brawny pattern offers an aggressive texture without the work or maintenance of grout lines. This mountainous and weathered texture makes a bold statement. Proline was the innovator of the seamless texture skins, made to overlap each other for a simple application. For easy installation, all Seamless Texture mats come with handles, with the exception of the touch up size. We offer this pattern in 6 varieties of size and density. See: 4BL, 3BL, 24BL, 2BL, 2BLF.

short_description: Size: 5' X 5' Tools: 5TR,4TR,3TR,24TR,2TR, 2TRF
summary: Travertine is a sedimentary rock. Extensive deposits are found in Tivoli, Italy. Travertine is a porous finish with numerous cavities. Proline can give you the look of this beautiful natural resource in a fraction of the cost. The Italians say "Il tempo e denoro" or "time is money". Why pay a high cost for imported stone, when Proline has replicated the same look with an easy to install application. Additionally, concrete is more durable, holds up to any conditions, and can be colored to your tailored needs. We offer this Seamless Texture in a variety of 6 sizes and flexibilities. See:4TR, 3TR, 24TR, 2TR, 2TRF.

As with all Proline Seamless Texture mats, with the exception of touch up mats, handles are included. We offer this pattern in 6 different sizes and flexes. See: 4FF, 3FF, 24FF, 2FF, 2FFF.

short_description: Tools: TTR1000
summary: Proline's Herringbone Tumbled Travertine features a unique texture within a Herringbone design. Featuring tumbled stone edges, this pattern consists of 8" x 16" paver tiles, laid out in a Herringbone pattern. The recessed grout lines and texture protect the antiquing, allowing the installer the choice of no sealer. This is but one of several new patterns featuring Proline's new Tumbled Travertine design.

short_description: Tools: TTR1200
summary: Proline recently came out with this new Tumbled Travertine texture, including this version set inside of a 12" x 12" square tile. Unlike any other texture, this Tumbled Travertine gives the installer the choice to grout the texture. The surface is flat with all the texture recessed, allowing the option of leaving the surface unsealed for a more natural look, perfect for a swimming pool area.

short_description: Tools: TTR1800
summary: One of Proline's new Tumbled Travertine patterns is this 18" x 18" square tile pattern. This new addition to the Proline collection is unique because it showcases a texture that can be grouted. The tiles have a tumbled edge. A flat surface with all the texture recessed gives this pattern a Travertine appearance and allows the concrete to go sealed or unsealed for a more natural look.

short_description: Tools: BW100,BW100F, BW110, BW120, SKW, W18F, HT12S, HTX24T
summary: Proline offers the look of wood flooring with the durability of concrete. Our Boardwalk is highly life-like, right down to the pegs in the planks. Each plank is 12" wide and comes in 4', 6' & 8' lengths. Use our new Water Based Acrylic Stains to color this pattern to your choice - brown tones for natural wood look. Color in gray tones and add our Wild Mustang Border Art for a true Western look. We also offer a 6" wood plank. See BW170.

summary: Proline manufactures the most life-like and beautiful wood planks in the market. This pattern consists of 6" wood planks "ganged" together in a staggered pattern. Each stamp has five rows of 6" wide planks. We suggest you include a "end cap" 6" wide and 4' long, offered in both the rigid and superflex material. At the end of each plank there are two peg holes for added reality. This lovely pattern adorns the Polar Bear exhibit at Sea World, San Diego. Use any of our beautiful Water Based Acrylic Stains and EZ-Tique Water Based Antiquing System colors to add your mark of distinction.

short_description: Size: 8" W x 5" H
summary: Of all insects, none elicit pleasure and curiosity more readily than the butterfly and are among the most beautiful and marvelous creatures in all of nature. Representations of butterflies are seen in Egytian frescoes, dating more than 3500 years ago. You too can add these beautiful and graceful creatures to any area, inside or out, with Proline's new Hand Sculpted Accent Pieces. We offer a set of three butterflies, however, each stamp is sold individually as well (see SA2000, SA2001 & SA2002). Very easy to install, these pieces are perfect to color with our new EZ-Accent Water Based Stains. Use them alone, or as a compliment to our Garden Rose Border Art

short_description: Size: 7.5" W x 7.5" H

This piece would also make a perfect addition to our Garden Rose or Hawaiian Flower Border Art Tools. Add Proline's Garden Stone - and viola - a perfect garden area is born! Sculpted edges let the pattern blend into the stamped concrete texture. Easy to install and inexpensive to buy, these pieces add a custom look to your home or business. Let your home express your whimsical side and create a masterpiece to make your neighbors envious.

short_description: Size: 8" x 6.5"H

In all cultures, they are considered fanciful and alluring. This Hand Sculpted Accent Piece is beautiful alone or as an accent to many of our other Proline pieces such as our Border Art series. Easy to stamp and simple to color with our new EZ-Accent Water Based Acrylic Stain.

summary: New! Seamless Design of Philodendron Leaf set inside a Seamless Texture. Seamless texture will match Roman Slate or Italian Slate. Overall stamp size is 36" x 32" with leaf measurement of 27" x 24".

short_description: Tools: Radial Color Code Stamp Layout
summary: This schematic shows the five tools in this series and how to lay them out for a large radial pattern. All tools in this series can be used individually or as a group series. Individually, they produce a circle, a serpentine, straight cobble or band tools. This is the first radial in the industry that will go our as far as the imagination. Proline has also designed a new Octagon Radial with the same capabilities.

summary: Proline has designed a new radial stamp, unline any on the market, that can create a radius of infinite dimensions with one affordable set of tools. Even more innovative, this stamp series can create a serpentine cobble, a straight cobble or several band tool designs. This piece, the Double Tool, will create a straight cobblestone by itself. This series is a remarkable value, due to the many looks you can create.

Proline offers over 150 styles of decorative stamps, including this line of European Fans. Proline offers three versions of the Fan- small stone, large stone and a Fishscale version.

Proline manufactures the finest Tampers in the market. This patented tool offers easy dismantel, an extra long grip, composite handle, removable locking pin, rounded corners and edges and self-aligning base. Most important, our Tampers have a shock-absorbing flexible coupling to take the pressure off the shoulders of the installer.

Proline is the innovator of the Seamless Texturing system. The very first Seamless Texture to roll out of a production line was Proline's Old Granite Cleft Stone. It was followed by Roman Slate, especially designed for Caesar Palace in Las Vegas. Now, these are the standards in the industry. All others are imitations of the original. All Proline skins are made of the highest grade urethane in a unique process that results in highly durable stamping tools. Proline tools are carefully hand-built and represent life-like stone and texture. As an applicator, you will appreciate how light and easy our mats are to use. All Seamless Textures include handles, with the exception of touch up mats

Proline offers over 150 styles of decorative stamps, including this line of Border Art. All Proline Border Art is made to fit within a 12" border. We offer looks for everyone's taste and motif - from our groundbreaking Grapevine to our stately Fleur-de-Lis. Proline is a very dynamic company and is continuously adding to this line. Border Art pieces are inexpensive, easy to apply and give your job a highly customized look. Also, these pieces are easily colored with Proline's new EZ-Accent water-based stain

Named after Bill Shorey "The Colorman" of Spec-West in Sacramento California, this hand tamper is small & lightweight yet it has Heavy-Duty construction. It can be used both horizontally & vertically. It's small size is perfect for tight areas and stairs.
This chisel has a hammered edge. Also, a standard (straight) edge is available.

Proline is the innovator of the Joint Texture Strips. These strips are designed to give your joints a hammered edge appearance. So simple to use by placing the strips inside your joint cuts, put a seamless texture on top and stamp with a tamper. Each strip is approx. 62" in length, 3/4" deep and 1 1/2" wide. We offer Joint Texture Strips in narrower & wider versions, as well
Touch up roller with a Stone texture 4.5" in length. Fits standart paint rollers handles. Handles not included. Also available in 9" length
